             was indicted for <rs id="t18301028-221-off1240" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18301028-221-off1240" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18301028-221-off1240" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18301028-221-cd1241" type="crimeDate">15th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-221-off1240 t18301028-221-cd1241"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18301028-221-victim1856" type="victimName">
                           George Kearsley 
                           Davison
                        <interp inst="t18301028-221-victim1856" type="surname" value="Davison"></interp>
